  "texts": [
    "At the paragraph-level, the paragraph identification function utilizes Bi-LSTMs to organize the contextual sentence representations into a paragraph structure.",
    "To predict both the sentence functions and paragraph functions, softmax is applied over the function representations.",
    "Finally, the organization quality of the essay is represented as a tensor representation that encompasses both sentence functions and paragraph functions.",
    "By applying CNN and max pooling over the tensor, a score for the organization trait is generated.",
    "Fig. 13 Hierarchical multi-task learning for organization evaluation architecture (Song et al. 2020a) Overall, this hierarchical multi-task learning approach enables the evaluation of the organizational quality of argumentative essays by optimizing sentence and paragraph functions, leading to improved assessment of the essays' organizational traits."
